Walking alongside a Child in Crisis

I Know We Have a Few Moments Left before We Go to the News Break What Would Be some of the Needs in Your Ministry Is There some Needs That You Have in the Ministry That We Can Help with that Are 3-Band Viewers at Home Can Help with What Are some of the Things That You'Re Looking for the Future May Be some Goals You Have and Then You Say Oh but We Have these Needs What Would Be some Things Well the Number One Absolutely Would Be Prayer

This Issue from Top to Bottom It's a Spiritual Issue because It Attacks the People Who Are Made in the Image of the Lord and the Evil One Has Deceived Us and He's Tricked Us into Accepting Lie and Believing It Is as Truth and So Truly People Praying that Is What Is Moving It's Moving People's Hearts It's Awakening People's Minds and People Who Before Were Silent They'Re Coming to Life Again and It's Absolutely Phenomenal and Glorious We Are Hoping that Bigger Venues in Terms of the Message Being Able To Get in Front of Women Get in Front of Men Get in Front of Pastors We'Ll Open Up and We See the Lord Doing that More and More Now You'Re Doing Women's Retreats You'Ve Done Yes Done Asi Spoken to Asi Oh I See Yes What Are some of the Other Venues They'Ve Been To Amen

Hello My Name Is Jd Quinn Manager of Three Append Pastoral Team Just Want To Thank You for all That You Do for Us We Thank You for Your Prayers Your Financial Support for Your Thoughtfulness Just Want To Take a Few Seconds Here Just To Kind Of Give You an Update of What's Going On in Our Department Number One We Have a Dedicated Staff To Pray for People around the World Who Call in Daily Perhaps They Just Need a Scriptural Reference Perhaps They Need Prayer Maybe It's a Word of Encouragement We Also Lead Them to the Local Sunday at His Church We Also Teach Them More about the Doctrine
